Package: svySE
Type: Package
Title: Sampling Error Estimation for Complex Surveys
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        given = "Luis",
        family = "Burgos",
        email = "lburgoss1996@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Estimates sampling errors for indicators from complex survey
    designs and produces unweighted simple indicator tables. Supports weighted
    totals, proportions, standard errors, confidence intervals, coefficients
    of variation, design effects, grouped and domain estimates, optional
    stratification and clustering variables, and customizable exports to
    '.xlsx' files.
